#

Creamy Mashed Potato Casserole

60 min
$10
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 8

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

Comfort FoodSide DishEasyCheesy

Description

A rich and creamy mashed potato casserole topped with cheese, perfect for a comforting side dish.

Ingredients

  • mashed potatoes: 4 cups
  • cream cheese: 8 oz
  • sour cream: 1 cup
  • shredded cheddar cheese: 1 cup
  • butter: 1/2 cup
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • green onions: 1/4 cup chopped (for garnish)
